And you can think about this
when you start your next version

00:09:19.256 --> 00:09:20.836 A:middle
of your app, you
shift to version 1,

00:09:20.836 --> 00:09:21.976 A:middle
you shift to version--
and I'm going

00:09:21.976 --> 00:09:23.826 A:middle
to start working on version 2.

00:09:24.196 --> 00:09:25.786 A:middle
You're marketing guy
