00:14:05.306 --> 00:14:07.056 A:middle
now you can control
drag between views

00:14:07.056 --> 00:14:08.746 A:middle
to add relationships
that are constraints.

00:14:09.226 --> 00:14:11.846 A:middle
So hold Control, I
can just could drag

