00:14:15.936 --> 00:14:18.436 A:middle
I'm going to pause again
and point out a few things.

00:14:18.986 --> 00:14:21.026 A:middle
When you add your first
constraint to a view,

00:14:21.026 --> 00:14:22.886 A:middle
what you're telling
Interface Builder is, "Hey,

00:14:22.886 --> 00:14:25.046 A:middle
I want to be in-charge
of the layout for this--

00:14:25.236 --> 00:14:27.666 A:middle
of this view," and now what
Interface Builder does is it

00:14:27.666 --> 00:14:30.796 A:middle
starts trying to help you,
by just pointing things out,

00:14:31.166 --> 00:14:33.146 A:middle
and just making sure that
you're getting the constraints

00:14:33.146 --> 00:14:33.896 A:middle
that you want.

00:14:34.526 --> 00:14:36.626 A:middle
So there's two things I want
to point out here: First,

00:14:36.896 --> 00:14:39.366 A:middle
the constraint that I've added,
I've only added one constraint,

00:14:39.366 --> 00:14:41.166 A:middle
and the constraint that
I've added is orange,

00:14:41.626 --> 00:14:44.266 A:middle
which is indicating to me "Hey,
I still have more work to do."

00:14:44.266 --> 00:14:47.536 A:middle
The other that Interface
Builder is doing is,

00:14:47.536 --> 00:14:49.806 A:middle
it's showing me my
Runtime Layout.

00:14:50.036 --> 00:14:54.126 A:middle
Like I said, with Xcode 5, you
can have your Design Time Layout

00:14:54.126 --> 00:14:56.306 A:middle
and your Runtime Layout be
different while you're building

00:14:56.566 --> 00:14:58.626 A:middle
as you get to the
point where you want

00:14:58.626 --> 00:14:59.636 A:middle
to have the UI that you want.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:15:00.076 --> 00:15:02.056 A:middle
And so, what Interface Builder
is showing me is, "OK, this is--

00:15:02.056 --> 00:15:05.466 A:middle
this big rectangle here is
where my Design Time Layout is,

00:15:06.026 --> 00:15:09.406 A:middle
and this dotted rectangle is
what the constraints would

00:15:09.406 --> 00:15:10.636 A:middle
generate at runtime."

00:15:12.106 --> 00:15:14.146 A:middle
And so what I can
do is if I control

00:15:14.146 --> 00:15:15.076 A:middle
and I got off the right edge,

